{"tid":2302202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"壹傳媒(00282.HK)曾急漲43%越50天線 以4.71億元售台灣物業","createTime":"2020-11-27T02:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T03:22:36.000Z","uid":74532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1399ef9fb4794fadc6aa5ff89f2d2e52b1bab2","tid":2302202,"uid":74532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"以4.71億元出售台灣物業，該股今早一舉升破五個移動平均線(百天及50天線分別位於0.24元及0.23元)，曾急漲43%高見0.305元，現造0.265元，急漲24%，成交急增至6,541萬股，涉資1,795萬元。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒公布，間接全資附屬壹傳媒傳訊播放股份有限公司作為賣方，與買方就建議出售一直用於營運台灣業務的物業簽訂意向書，總代價金額為17.5億元新台幣(相當於約4.71億港元)。公司認為，出售所得款項將增強公司現金流，營運資金狀況亦可改善，從而可為日後發展重新調配旗下資源。<br />\n<br />\n加油呀肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce3a6d78968282f2e54eb814a875d3e7906573","tid":2302202,"uid":257347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"台灣果邊都蝕緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea607fcf279853e75dddd44d7f8c428e4fa1450b","tid":2302202,"uid":74532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05ce3a6d78968282f2e54eb814a875d3e7906573","tid":2302202,"uid":257347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"台灣果邊都蝕緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"好難捱呀，黑警又成日搞佢"},{"pid":"5ad4bdb3a3777eaa6006ab0423e2c02b67252c33","tid":2302202,"uid":24576,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"準備破產啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456de44c8911b90d7c14708a9d92c9511c9c31f1","tid":2302202,"uid":74532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"#4邊位？睇唔到"},{"pid":"406454e3c167c8cbd0743d61008b0e5b8b0e4fa9","tid":2302202,"uid":64874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎自己都講過已經墊支借錢畀壹傳媒，方向報成日J呢樣嘢，吹到壹傳媒好快執。<br />\n<br />\n不過最大問題係壹傳媒未搵到網上傳媒嘅profit model,結果維持紙媒規模去搞網媒，呢樣先最致命。"}]}